Cookie Preferences

We use cookies (or similar) to measure our audience, enhance your browsing experience and provide you with ads on this and other sites.

By clicking YES, you agree to such purposes and the collection and sharing of your data with our partner(s). You can find out more, manage your preferences and withdraw your consent at any time.

Manage Cookie Preferences

We use cookies to help you navigate efficiently and perform certain functions. You will find detailed information about all cookies under each consent category below.

          Deluxe Room

          35sqm

          Choice of a King-sized Bed or Twin Beds

          Wireless Wi-Fi

          Room Details

          Offering picturesque views of the city and the Red River, our Deluxe Room features a stylish bathroom with a refreshing shower and premium amenities, making it one of the best accommodations among hotels in Hanoi Vietnam. An in-room entertainment system with local and international channels adds to your enjoyment, while a thoughtful workspace enables you to handle your professional matters with ease.

          In-room Amenities

          For Your Comfort
          • A choice of king-sized bed or twin beds
          • Executive writing table and stationery set
          • Energy-efficient air-conditioning system
          • Bathrobes, slippers and hairdryer
          For Your Indulgence
          • LCD television with local and cable channels
          • Tea and coffee making facilities
          • Complimentary bottled mineral water
          • Fully stocked minibar
          For Your Convenience
          • Complimentary Internet access
          • IDD telephone and voicemail
          • Secured key-card access
          • In-room safe
